// *******************************************************************************************
//
// → Why Create Unit Tests?
//
//   It's simple really. It proves that our code really does work by checking it!
//
//   It's horrible when users complain about bugs with features we created oursekves.
//   It almost feels shameful sometimes. But let's fear not.. unit tests can save us.
//
//   Unit tests are lilke having an entire testing team just for yourself. Except their
//   results are almost instantaneous, delivering immediate reassurance that the app
//   behaves as it was designed to.
//
//   Unit tests exist for us, the developers. They are our tools. What amazing tools
//   they are too. Our unit tests save us so much time revealing and killing bugs.
//
//   They are just great.
//   We recommend writing some. 👍
//
// *******************************************************************************************
